			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="48" color="#ffffff">全技能一图流</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#a081f3" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="63" y="660" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#a3a5fe" width="313" height="43" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" color="#a3a5fe">受塑的已死之龙</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#a081f3" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1786" y="48" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="30" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="218" height="34" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.5019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="right" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="30" color="#ffffff">元素能量：NA</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#a081f3" distance="10" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="61" y="566" fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="24" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="355" height="30" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="24" fontStyle="italic" color="#ffffff">Lord of Eroded Primal Fire</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#a081f3" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="64" y="708" fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="20" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#a3a5fe" width="281" height="25" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="20" fontStyle="italic" color="#a3a5fe">The Slain Dragon Molded</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#a081f3" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="503" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特召唤4枚拟视之实，依次朝玩家扔来，每枚造成<span color="#b8b8b8">40%,10%,4% </span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">10</span><span>)伤害；拟视之实爆炸留下持续20s的渊泥，每0.5s造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">5%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">2</span><span>)伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1200" width="468" height="116" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">拟覆叶：<span color="#bfbfff">3虚界</span><span>盾，破盾后击败，一共有3个，全部击败后可令古斯托特瘫痪15s，并扣除古斯托特</span><span color="#ffdfbf">10%</span><span>生命值。<br/>虚界护罩：成功破除后扣除古斯托特</span><span color="#ffdfbf">10%</span><span>生命值。<br/><br/>坠入平台之下时，会传送回场地中央，但前台角色将会扣除</span><span color="#ffdfbf">80%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="991" width="482" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">低于<span color="#ffccbf">65%</span><span>生命值时，古斯托特释放寰宇界门，倾下数十秒的沦没黑雨，雨滴造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">15%,<br/>3.75%,1.5%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">5</span><span>)伤害；黑雨间夹杂间断的淤块，淤块造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">35%,8.75%,3.5%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">15</span><span>)伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1474" y="991" width="499" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特遁入黑霾之夜，并召唤3个<span textDecoration="underline">拟覆叶</span><span>发射白蜡叶，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">10%,1%</span><span>伤害；黑夜持续12s；若未及时破坏所有的拟覆叶，则古斯托特将施放「霾中迷物罟中沉」。开战技后的</span><span color="#ff9999">火神</span><span>和</span><span color="#ffbfbf">火主</span><span>可以立即驱散黑霾。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1474" y="735" width="499" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">技能「虬首孤月染<span fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans">赩</span><span>潮」超时未破盾时，古斯托特将手搓的量子奇点掷向玩家，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">60%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">30</span><span>)伤害并留下渊泥。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1474" y="1247" width="499" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特锁定在场玩家，片刻后伸出黑爪，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">40%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">20</span><span>)伤害，紧接黑爪握拳，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">60%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">30</span><span>)伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1474" y="223" width="506" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特举起斫阳之曜，重重进行下劈，造成大范围<span color="#ff9999">60%</span><span>伤害并留下3处持续20s的余烬，每0.5s造成</span><span color="#ff9999">10%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1474" y="479" width="489" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特使用斫阳之曜进行左划、右划2段普攻，均造成大范围<span color="#ff9999">30%</span><span>伤害并留下余烬。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1247" width="502" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">继「沧<span fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans">睱</span><span>黑雨天刀燎」后，古斯托特凝聚日炎之力，使用斫阳之曜沿中心圆切线方向切开场地，造成大范围</span><span color="#ff9999">120%</span><span>伤害。该技能最多施放3次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="499" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特使用斫阳之曜对玩家进行一次冲击，造成大范围<span color="#ff9999">60%</span><span>伤害并留下余烬，然后闪现到玩家背后，并随机接上「千曜焚灭晨昏现」或「刀锋过焰寂沉消」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="484" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特将斫阳之曜插入地面,持续产生焰浪，造成<span color="#ff9999">20%,5%,2%</span><span>伤害，技能期间古斯托特持有13s的</span><span textDecoration="underline">虚界护罩</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
